00:55:37,131 --> 00:55:41,260
Rym: So they had the oak table removed from the room, and suddenly everything went back to normal.

794
00:55:42,320 --> 00:55:42,521
Scott: Yeah.

795
00:55:42,964 --> 00:55:45,420
Scott: So, that's called crazy people.

796
00:55:45,860 --> 00:55:53,679
Rym: Now, the best part is, all of these people, if you subject them to a double blind test, wherein they don't know what stereo system they're listening to...

797
00:55:54,321 --> 00:55:56,464
