798
00:55:56,484 --> 00:55:57,625
Scott: You blindfold someone.

799
00:55:58,006 --> 00:55:59,268
Scott: You put them in a room.

800
00:55:59,628 --> 00:56:02,132
Scott: You then turn a stereo on playing song.

801
00:56:02,512 --> 00:56:05,437
Scott: You then change to the other stereo playing the same song.

802
00:56:05,777 --> 00:56:07,880
Scott: You then ask them which one sounded better.

803
00:56:08,020 --> 00:56:17,040
